</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="196" pageNumber="958" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="196.[177,1384,2183,3480]" pageId="196" pageNumber="958">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[177,411,3289,3322]" pageId="196" pageNumber="958">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
On Sanana, Peters’s Dorsal has been seen flying out of village houses, suggesting it may roost in houses. In 
<collectingCountry box="[728,850,3329,3362]" name="Vietnam" pageId="196" pageNumber="958">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
, one was found roosting in a young banana leaf.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
